description:
Brad Burns (ブラッド・バーンズ - Buraddo Bānzu) is the main character from Green Blood, he is from Ireland and about 20-21 years old. By the time the history takes place Brad lives in New York with his brother Luke Burns. He is the son of Edward King and Alicia Burns.

Brad appears in the first chapter of Green Blood #1.
name: Brad Burns

description: Character from Green Blood, he is the father of Brad and Luke Burns, Edward King is missing. The desire of Brad Burns is to find and kill his father.
name: Edward King

description:
Luke Burns (ルーク・バーンズ - Rūku Bānzu) is a character from Green Blood. He is the younger brother of Brad Burns. Luke is about 16-17 years old and live together with his brother. While Brad works for the Grave Diggers, Luke manages to gain some money with honest and common jobs.

His first appearance is in chapter 1 from Green Blood #1
name: Luke Burns

description: Hawk (ホーク - Hōku) is a character from Green Blood. He appears in the cover of volume 4, along with Swallow, Dodo, , Parrot, Eagle and Edward King. He is a member of The Crimson Gang and his first appearance was in chapter 24.
